com.simiacryptus.mindseye.net.dag

Class DAGNetwork

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.simiacryptus.mindseye.net.NNLayer
      • com.simiacryptus.mindseye.net.dag.DAGNetwork
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DAGNode, Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    PipelineNetwork, SupervisedNetwork

    public abstract class DAGNetwork
extends NNLayer
implements DAGNode
    Builds a network NNLayer components, assumed to form a directed acyclic graph with a single output. Supplied builder methods designed to build linear sequence of units acting on the current output node.
    Author:
    Andrew Charneski
